| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5534 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 15c29a63-e945-526b-9d90-8f890cd7ca11"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
